78 void testCheckPackVoltagecellVoltageandcurrentSensorBothZero(void) {
79  int32_t packVoltage_mV = 0;
80  int32_t highVoltage_mV = 0;
81  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(PL_CheckStringVoltage(packVoltage_mV, highVoltage_mV), STD_OK);
82 }

90 void testCheckPackVoltagecellVoltageandcurrentSensorDifferenceEqualsTolerance(void) {
